      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:24:3",
      "text": [
        " امْرَأَةٍ افْتَضَّتْ جَارِيَةً بِيَدِهَا قَالَ عَلَيْهَا مَهْرُهَا وَ تُجْلَدُ ثَمَانِينَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Najran, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> regarding a woman who deflowered a slave girl by her hand. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Upon her is her dower, and she would be whipped eighty lashes’."
        ]
      }
